{"tid":1130334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗官陳茂波係咪會遺臭萬年？","createTime":"2019-04-29T03:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T04:49:42.000Z","uid":214261,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b0fae39049526044540ce65ed552e45fa7ecd86e","tid":1130334,"uid":214261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:20:25.000Z","msg":"真心未見過有人做官係垃圾方面做得咁出色<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波on9事件一覽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">誹謗訴訟\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涉嫌在新界東北發展計劃有利益衝突\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涉嫌經營劏房及避稅事件</span></span>\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">酒後駕駛\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不小心駕駛\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藐視立法會議員資格\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">涉以離岸公司隱瞞資產\t<br />\n<br />\n[size=5][red]翻新財政司官邸\t</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乘坐紅色跑車出席公務員喪禮</span></span>\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">派錢4千，職津處請唔夠合約工 多人難抵「捽數」 劈炮</span></span><br />\n政府向合資格人士派發4,000元的「關愛共享計劃」，涉及高達3億元行政費，但計劃推出以來，行政管理混亂，申請手續繁複擾民，審批程序又緩慢。負責的職津處直至本月中才聘足700名員工，惟有相關計劃的合約員工透露，人手仍嚴重不足，管理層要求員工「跑數」，每人每日需輸入250份申請表及發放通知短訊，不少人經已離職。工會預計，聘請困難加上員工「劈炮」，未來情況將更為混亂，隨時影響市民領取4,000元。<br />\n<br />\n不過人無恥則無敵<br />\n為左一毫子可以賣白粉<br />\n仲有咩做唔出？<br />\n佢應該都有哂心理準備俾人唾罵先夠膽咁做"},{"pid":"4fdde7a8746e4d127fc9bf5397c4fd2e5a58f459","tid":1130334,"uid":157983,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:22:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5181503851322020a9adfa8fa3e3f0c449e6b72","tid":1130334,"uid":60057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"你仲記唔記得上幾手啲狗官?"},{"pid":"1090366351b96cded6706a3b0d04b18b08e8e3c3","tid":1130334,"uid":40226,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"唔好講笑啦大把人根本唔知政府有幾狗西<br />\n好似我老豆老母<br />\n政府一定係好<br />\n反政府一定係衰<br />\n好喺邊衰喺邊又講唔出<br />\n連人反緊咩都唔知就屌人搞亂檔<br />\n儒家文化真係遺禍萬年"},{"pid":"96b9232a96ae1e3e9910150b03b1667c6837061a","tid":1130334,"uid":152598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T03:58:04.000Z","msg":"一定會"},{"pid":"3bdd2c05b3da0fd47f06e5d20c6678e04adeb74a","tid":1130334,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"mpf 高鐵 普教中果班狗官都冇人記得"},{"pid":"fcefc633be6b95d4f86415ff519363f0f933f864","tid":1130334,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T04:49:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你就想<br />\n佢升得快過火箭<br />\n分分鐘下屆特首<br />\n記住！佢唔係服務市民</span>"}]}